name: #2-2 Thara (The Four Fairies)
description:
This is a separate sub-collection of my Dream Dolls Collection. Glad to introduce "Thara".

My dream today is cool because today I met the fairy of the river "Thara".

Thara has hair as a stream of clear water. It flowed in the forest floating in the air. So beautiful, I told myself. 

Tara was kind. She smiled at me and floated away with a beautiful stream. Wonderful Dream :-)
